item.title: CVE-2016-9928|2024-08-06T03:07:31.382Z -- mcabber -- mcabber
item.description: MCabber before 1.0.4 is vulnerable to roster push attacks, which allows remote attackers to intercept communications, or add themselves as an entity on a 3rd party's roster as another user, which will also garner associated privileges, via crafted XMPP packets.
